title: QB/TE Tiers | The Ringer Fantasy Football Show
description:
From the guys who brought you the Dantasy Football Podcast, it's The Ringer Fantasy Football Show! Follow us on our own feed here on Spotify!
We talk through our quarterback and tight end tiers and point out the players we like the most, and the players who should be relegated to the tier below.

QB Tiers
Tier 1 (5:31)
Tier 2 (6:45)
Tier 3 (13:11)
Tier 4 (17:30)
Tier 5 (23:55)

Tight End Tiers
Tier 1 (32:32)
Tier 2 (33:08)
Tier 3 (35:07)
Tier 4 (41:21)
Tier 5 (49:47)

Check out The Ringer Fantasy Football Guide for a closer look at our tiers, rankings, and more.

Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
